    "description": "<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >&quot;其中都包括什么？</h2></strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色：疯狂汽车秀：斯蒂格挑战</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186050/extras/809fcdbfafe9762828d16bbe7ddc5510.poster.avif?t=1698695641\" width=604 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186050/extras/809fcdbfafe9762828d16bbe7ddc5510.webm?t=1698695641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186050/extras/809fcdbfafe9762828d16bbe7ddc5510.mp4?t=1698695641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>加入新排行榜：疯狂汽车秀：斯蒂格挑战，新的坡道、跷跷板、隧道以及更多组合添加到疯狂汽车秀测试赛道，让你的技能受到终极考验！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >排行榜轮换</h2>在每个挑战的排行榜上竞争你的时间得分。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >新的游乐场</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186050/extras/cdd8eaa8a15f2c4c12c04dadcb374b94.poster.avif?t=1698695641\" width=604 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186050/extras/cdd8eaa8a15f2c4c12c04dadcb374b94.webm?t=1698695641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186050/extras/cdd8eaa8a15f2c4c12c04dadcb374b94.mp4?t=1698695641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>实验物理学和速度，以达到排行榜的顶端！每辆汽车和挑战的组合都会带来不同的挑战，并将你的技能测试到极限。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >受节目启发的经典之作登上赛道</h2><strong>坚不可摧的皮卡</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186050/extras/79e3590458bf2a6355b40b54db6b50a6.poster.avif?t=1698695641\" width=604 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186050/extras/79e3590458bf2a6355b40b54db6b50a6.webm?t=1698695641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186050/extras/79e3590458bf2a6355b40b54db6b50a6.mp4?t=1698695641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>這種有彈性的 Pick Up 可以翻滾、旋轉和滾動——無論你把它放在什麼地方，它都會繼續前進！ Indestructible Pick Up 可以添加到任何自定義大廳或在免費遊戲中與 AI 比賽。坚不可摧的皮卡可以被添加到任何自定义大厅或在自由游戏中与AI比赛。<br><br><strong>火箭！</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186050/extras/97d85826eb413275c96da45f55d414ba.poster.avif?t=1698695641\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186050/extras/97d85826eb413275c96da45f55d414ba.webm?t=1698695641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186050/extras/97d85826eb413275c96da45f55d414ba.mp4?t=1698695641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>当你可以用3个轮子比赛时，谁还需要4个轮子？火箭加入比赛，哦，孩子，我们不确定它们是否应该参加比赛，但我们现在无法阻止它们。火箭可以被添加到任何自定义大厅或在自由游戏中与AI比赛。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你们要求的，我们也想要，就这么定了：拖车加入比赛！</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186050/extras/238928a268e930fc83ee498071bf1e4c.poster.avif?t=1698695641\" width=604 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186050/extras/238928a268e930fc83ee498071bf1e4c.webm?t=1698695641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186050/extras/238928a268e930fc83ee498071bf1e4c.mp4?t=1698695641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>赛车很有趣，但是在你的车尾挂着一辆拖车的情况下，赛车就更有趣了！在疯狂汽车秀：斯蒂格挑战DLC里，你可以在自由游戏和自定义大厅中为汽车添加拖车。",
